{"tid":442064,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"東歐團12日行程求建議！！","createTime":"2017-10-20T09:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T09:08:40.000Z","uid":42848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b9cc4756179e1cdb1adab0834fdeaa9dd10538ea","tid":442064,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T09:14:38.000Z","msg":"2.5日布拉格，3日krakow，3日布達佩斯，2.5日維也納<br />\n自問唔多好歷史音樂，比較好睇自然景觀，古典建築，2.5日維也納會唔會太多，好唔好分1日比salzburg?大<br />\n同埋布拉格都好唔好 分1日即日來回ck?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe0a98beb1444bbcebd0ad723dcbb2ae0719004","tid":442064,"uid":44377,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T09:17:22.000Z","msg":"唔好音樂, 1 日維也納都俾多"},{"pid":"e831d4b8d30bfd128d8e217f76ba0264992fe25b","tid":442064,"uid":7173,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T09:55:45.000Z","msg":"Salzburg好撚悶"},{"pid":"8608098beeca6627185fd2825c3cdd3f89547bf9","tid":442064,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T09:56:34.000Z","msg":"不如分俾Hallstatt仲好"},{"pid":"cccc38d1874ae8242e7d71f2703776ee7913d84c","tid":442064,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T10:36:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如分俾Hallstatt仲好</blockquote><br />\n去過，住咗一晚好正(又好重皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，夜晚走咗出去兩次湖邊睇星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9a0c6391d56d9d3cc269bfe9e0630b8f6fd947","tid":442064,"uid":98068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T10:41:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Salzburg好撚悶</blockquote><br />\n睇你購唔購物，果邊shopping平"},{"pid":"a6713d3d74d7c6205e590e78af5d7a079c2316d9","tid":442064,"uid":98068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T10:43:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如分俾Hallstatt仲好</blockquote><br />\n當年我即日來回，係好值得去<br />\n<br />\n但一定一定要住意尾班車，果度得一架巴士，但行幾條線！<br />\n<br />\n上次我miss左要坐150車番薩爾斯堡"},{"pid":"39ff0f5ba5faf0eada67b295e005cbc0ec5c0f23","tid":442064,"uid":98068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T10:47:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不如分俾Hallstatt仲好</blockquote><br />\n當年我即日來回，係好值得去<br />\n<br />\n但一定一定要住意尾班車，果度得一架巴士，但行幾條線！<br />\n<br />\n上次我miss左要坐150eur車費(的士追尾班火車)番薩爾斯堡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n布拉格地鐵有分外城同內城飛，唔好貪平買錯外城飛，d查飛狗專捉遊客，捉到就罰錢，我果陣仲要累左4個fd一齊比人捉<br />\n同記得打飛，冇打都罰"},{"pid":"7168392a225bf52971b5fb46118fd22649e1883f","tid":442064,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T10:49:27.000Z","msg":"咁趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f19af04a8fdc262872b125f750bbc97058379d","tid":442064,"uid":98068,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T10:53:07.000Z","msg":"布達佩斯反而我覺得冇咩好行<br />\n<br />\nck即日來回好趕喎，來回5個幾鐘車程<br />\n<br />\n去ck可以bk騎馬，冇人拖住住馬，你自己騎，跟住教練隻馬，前後都有人睇住<br />\n<br />\n唔貴幾好玩"},{"pid":"0190d2b67c86f305ca42f544c3d09508ca235e31","tid":442064,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:01:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>布達佩斯反而我覺得冇咩好行<br />\n<br />\nck即日來回好趕喎，來回5個幾鐘車程<br />\n<br />\n去ck可以bk騎馬，冇人拖住住馬，你自己騎，跟住教練隻馬，前後都有人睇住<br />\n<br />\n唔貴幾好玩</blockquote><br />\n波蘭同布達佩斯都係貪物價低先留耐啲，布達佩斯又係貪佢景靚夠懶洋洋先留幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲掙扎緊去唔去ck，唔肯定布拉格1日半夠唔夠自己行，到時ck搭去krakow轉車煩，仲要洗多幾歐(睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f11dff9c97e83f8666f84b93cf35ca3612b3593","tid":442064,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:02:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無計啦 係得呢12日連續都得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1339f570291bb30a8946c7e01a2157d90ecff50","tid":442064,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:08:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>布達佩斯反而我覺得冇咩好行<br />\n<br />\nck即日來回好趕喎，來回5個幾鐘車程<br />\n<br />\n去ck可以bk騎馬，冇人拖住住馬，你自己騎，跟住教練隻馬，前後都有人睇住<br />\n<br />\n唔貴幾好玩</blockquote><br />\n波蘭同布達佩斯都係貪物價低先留耐啲，布達佩斯又係貪佢景靚夠懶洋洋先留幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲掙扎緊去唔去ck，唔肯定布拉格1日半夠唔夠自己行，到時ck搭去krakow轉車煩，仲要洗多幾歐(睇student agency平flixbus4歐，但係凌晨兩點係轉車站等3個鐘轉車)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3664c9622c1da310ecfe6de42c3ae96fa1a66da7","tid":442064,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44182c54c13e9a8173097735d4218e15390d7db","tid":442064,"uid":16697,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T17:45:51.000Z","msg":"垃圾Wien<br />\nSalzburg 好撚好玩喔<br />\nUnterburg hellbrunn <br />\n附近仲有konigssee , st wolf gang ,  cave <br />\nHallsatt - salt mine, Gosausee , 5 finger ice cave"},{"pid":"aff0fcdd4252435f31211bfb1f1dae87e6acf212","tid":442064,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T18:13:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾Wien<br />\nSalzburg 好撚好玩喔<br />\nUnterburg hellbrunn <br />\n附近仲有konigssee , st wolf gang ,  cave <br />\nHallsatt - salt mine, Gosausee , 5 finger ice cave</blockquote><br />\n買咗wien回程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nkonigssee，hallstatt都去咗，係幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39be16e578da3d433ee255c2b1512d01143aad2e","tid":442064,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T18:43:56.000Z","msg":"budapest好玩 之前玩足七日<br />\nck值得去<br />\n維也納 多數朋友都叫中伏（佢地麻麻classical music"},{"pid":"f6b7c9c5f3cbfa8186f30546fb5d3288732238c4","tid":442064,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T18:44:24.000Z","msg":"布拉格1.5日其實差唔多架啦"},{"pid":"6fd2e160ad22f9cfc287afbf938e57ead4db8eb8","tid":442064,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T19:00:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>budapest好玩 之前玩足七日<br />\nck值得去<br />\n維也納 多數朋友都叫中伏（佢地麻麻classical music</blockquote><br />\n諗住維也納一日朝早行森林，一日行市中心睇建築，盡量hea行低消費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a7a8f89d0f35aad12d2c20a7829f13da2582e06","tid":442064,"uid":37803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:00:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>布拉格1.5日其實差唔多架啦</blockquote><br />\nagger"},{"pid":"2203497fa9c7d0d75b2dad1472dd775412c5fbdc","tid":442064,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T03:29:47.000Z","msg":"奧斯威辛幾值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f81b57ee8f859f645dc01b406d6ac8b1c0a00c9","tid":442064,"uid":36432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T03:38:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奧斯威辛幾值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪Krakow去到，仲有個鹽礦去玩㗎<br />\n<br />\n同埋有冇諗過去Cesky Krumlov? 雖然好多強國同泡菜，但成個地方都幾靚下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f7c87e9d4acddfe4a3c67a5258fc1c7622eeb1","tid":442064,"uid":114088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:01:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好音樂, 1 日維也納都俾多</blockquote><br />\n皇宮咪靚囉，洗唔洗咁趕<br />\n<br />\n維也納2日，布拉格2日，cesky krumlov 2日，布達佩斯2日，krakow 2日<br />\n<br />\n仲有2日俾時間做交通／buffer<br />\n<br />\n其實prague, budapest, krakow都好似樣，你會睇厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nsalzburg好天都ok嘅，我都覺得半日～1日夠"},{"pid":"84bffb7b52892eded82df70e69a68a78eeceb68a","tid":442064,"uid":9942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-